{"id": 225020946, "title": "New boutique hotel and apartments to open in Prestwick this summer", "text": "A new boutique hotel is set to open in Prestwick above the town's legendary Taj Bar & Kitchen. Situated on Main Street, DeiRa Hotel and Apartments will operate as a 10 room luxury offering located in the heart of the town and is set to open in July. Expected to be rated 4-stars, bosses say DeiRa is set to offer guests a \"first-class experience\" with luxurious fixtures and fittings, and elegantly designed rooms. It is the latest venture by the owners of Taj Bar & Kitchen, the restaurant that has been a beloved fixture in Prestwick for over 40 years. Perry Uppal, owner of DeiRa and Taj, said: \"We've been working on something really special for a while and we're absolutely delighted to announce that our fabulous new premises 'DeiRa Hotel & Apartments' will be opening this summer. \"With a focus on location, luxury, and the five-star customer service that has been a staple of our Taj offering since day one, we can't wait to reveal full details in the coming weeks. \"It really is the perfect spot for a romantic getaway or a golfing trip on the Ayrshire Coast.\" Read next: Ayr Station Hotel owner Sunny Ung breaks silence and halts demolition work Plan for former Kilmarnock Aulds the Bakers store unveiled as new store proposed Lidl unveils new Ayrshire store locations on 'wishlist' plan Mum 'worried' at kids not receiving hot meal in nurseries Ayrshire hotel named best in the region at national awards ceremony Don't miss the latest Ayrshire headlines \u2013sign up to our free daily newsletter", "summary": "DeiRa Hotel and Apartments will be a 10-room 'luxury boutique hotel' in the heart of the town", "url": "https://www.dailyrecord.co.uk/ayrshire/new-boutique-hotel-apartments-open-32916108", "image": "https://i2-prod.dailyrecord.co.uk/incoming/article32916074.ece/ALTERNATES/s1200/0_CCR_AP_290524DeiRaJPG.jpg", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-05-29 13:01:09", "au